headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Ubermacht Sentinel Classic
content: New to the dirt tracks of San Andreas, the Ubermacht Sentinel Classic has a little something for everybody it’s got the ego of a road-legal vintage sports car and the id of a no-nonsense street racer. But if you want to see it really shine, you’re just a stripped-out interior and some pop-up headlights away from taking it off-road and never looking back. Yes – it has the superego of a maniac.
